summary:
üë©‚Äçüéì Originally from France, I moved to the Netherlands five years ago to pursue a Bachelor in European Law at Maastricht University and a Masters in Private European Law at the University of Amsterdam. 

ü§ñ I have been lucky enough to gather professional experiences from different fields, including academic research, IT, social consulting and language teaching. I believe this eclectic background gives me an edge, as I have acquired a wide and varied set of skills.

üìä I am currently a consultant and auditor at EY CertifyPoint, the certification body of EY. Together with our multicultural team, we audit clients from all over the world against various standards including ISO27001, ISO27701, ISO9001, HDS etc

I am always excited to expand my network with like-minded professionals, lets connect !
